# ğŸ“¡ Multiuser Localization with Leaky-Wave Antennas (LWA)

This repository contains the full Python implementation used in the thesis:

**â€œMultiuser Localization with Leaky-Wave Antennasâ€ (Yoni Bartal, BGU 2025)**

The project implements signal-processing algorithms for **THz-band localization** using **Leaky-Wave Antennas** (LWAs), exploiting their natural **frequencyâ€“angle coupling** for single- and multi-user angle-of-arrival (AoA) estimation.

The repository includes:

- Maximum Likelihood (ML) estimator  
- Correlation-based LWA beamforming  
- LWAâ€“MUSIC (frequency-manifold MUSIC)  
- CRB derivations (numeric + analytic)  
- Single-user + multi-user simulations  
- Comparison vs. ULA beamforming  
- High-resolution pseudospectrum visualization  

